# Stationery Ordering Platform

A bilingual stationery ordering app built with Next.js 16, React 19, Prisma 7, and SQLite. It includes a customer shop, invite-code checkout, and a separate admin dashboard for orders, analytics, and fulfillment.

## Features

### Customer Shop

- Product catalog with category filtering and search
- Traditional Chinese and English UI
- Product detail pages with variant and size selection
- Cart drawer plus full cart page
- Checkout with pickup or delivery fulfillment
- Invite-code login required at checkout
- Order confirmation and status page

### Admin Dashboard

- Separate admin login with signed session cookie
- Dashboard metrics for orders, pending work, revenue, and daily activity
- Recharts-based analytics
- Order list and order detail views
- Five-step order status workflow:
  `PENDING_PAYMENT` -> `PENDING_VERIFICATION` -> `PENDING_SHIPMENT` -> `PENDING_PICKUP` -> `COMPLETED`
- Fulfillment views for pending shipments, stock shortages, and picking lists
- Product catalog management view

## Tech Stack

| Area | Technology |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 16 App Router |
| UI | React 19 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 4 |
| Database | Prisma 7 + SQLite |
