## Development Notes

- This project uses Next.js 16. Check `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before changing routing, proxy, or server APIs.
- Route protection uses `src/proxy.ts`; there is no `middleware.ts`.
- Cart state is client-side and persisted with `localStorage`.
- Order item names, SKUs, variants, and prices are snapshot at purchase time.
- SQLite is suitable for local development and simple single-server deployments.
- Do not commit `.env` or hardcode credentials.

## CI

The GitHub Actions workflow in `.github/workflows/ci.yml` runs install, Prisma generation, linting, type checking, and production build checks for pushes and pull requests.
